                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1r">Fol. 1r</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1r: ለዛቲ᎓ መጽሐፍ᎓ ዘአጽሐፋ᎓ አቤቶ᎓ ተክለ᎓ እግዚእ᎓ በእንተ᎓ ሕይወተ᎓ ነፍሱ᎓ ለወልደ᎓ ሚካኤል᎓ ወለብእሲቱ᎓ ሰበነ᎓ ጊዮርጊስ᎓ ወለደቂቁ᎓ ፀዳለ᎓ ማርያም᎓ ጸበለ᎓ ጊዮርጊስ᎓ ወወሀባ᎓ ለታቦተ᎓ ኪዳነ᎓ ምሕረት᎓ ደብረ᎓ ገነት᎓ ...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1r: The one who had this book written and who donated it to the tabot of Däbrä Gännät Kidanä Mǝḥrät is ʾabeto Täklä ʾƎgziʾ, for the sake of the life of the soul of Wäldä Mikaʾel and his wife Säbänä Giyorgis and his children Ḍädalä Maryam, Ṣäbälä Giyorgis … </q>
                           
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#19v">Fol. 19v</locus>: A miracle of Mary (?)<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 19v: ወሀሎ᎓ ፩ብእሲ᎓ ገባራ[sic]᎓ ወኮነ᎓ ያፈቅራ᎓ ለእግዚእትነ᎓ ማርያም᎓… </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 19v: There was a man … that loved our Lady Mary … </q>
                           
                        </item>
